  transition: transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.31, 1); }

  position: absolute;
  overflow: hidden;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  top: 0;
  visibility: hidden; }
  .ptr__pull-down > div {
    display: none; }
